</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">1 Summon: Elemental Defender (40m) - defense, goes in range slot or back slot ( I assume pet can only have one since it is lore, I have read in these forums of people giving them 2, one for each slot. But that doesn't make sense since it is lore. ). </td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
