				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Well, I wanna thank ya'll for the advice on Seafury Cyclops.
<br />

<br />
I was 90% into 48, just let a craptastic LDoN group and was looking for that last 10% for new spell level. So while I was logged off, I came here to see if I could find some advice.
<br />

<br />
I logged back in, popped myself over to OoT and took out a few Seafury Cyclops and bam, level 49 I was. At 48, with the 44 pet, I would pull with malaisment and nuke / heal as need. However, I discovered that our level 49 Fire pet (with Torch focus, set of plate armor and BO3) could solo a cyclops with no problem. EASY exp and decent loot. I was there for about 30 minutes and cleared over 400pp. A KEI, drogmor and Virtue made it almost too easy.</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
